    "Section 3 presents the research strategy followed in this work.",
    "Section 4 describes point cloud formation technologies, including a brief comparison between them.",
    "Section 5 focuses on the relationship between computer vision and point clouds, presenting DL methods on 3D point clouds, and various challenges.",
    "Section 6 reviews the literature on point cloud learnable methods and techniques for main vision tasks.",
    "Section 7 summarizes available point cloud datasets."
